                    <li>✓ Mobile-First Optimization</li>
                    <li>✓ SEO Technical Foundation</li>
                    <li>✓ Contact Form Integration</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">Get Started</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Tier 2 -->
            <div class="pricing-tier" style="border: 1px solid #3b82f6; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); position: relative; display: flex; flex-direction: column; transform: scale(1.02);">
                <div style="position: absolute; top: -10px; right: 20px; background: #3b82f6; color: #fff; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;">RECOMMENDED</div>
                <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #fff;">Full Website</h4>
                <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #3b82f6;">$7,500<span style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 400;">/project</span></div>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-grow: 1;">Complete digital presence with CMS and advanced functionality.</p>
                <ul style="list-style: none; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0;">
                    <li>✓ 5-10 Unique Page Templates</li>
                    <li>✓ CMS Integration (Shopify/Sanity)</li>
                    <li>✓ Advanced Analytics Setup</li>
                    <li>✓ Performance Optimization (90+ Score)</li>
                    <li>✓ 30 Days Post-Launch Support</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn btn-blue" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">Start Project</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Tier 3 -->
            <div class="pricing-tier" style="border: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #fff;">Custom Web App</h4>
                <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #3b82f6;">Custom<span style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 400;">/quote</span></div>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-grow: 1;">Complex logic, user accounts, and database integrations.</p>
                <ul style="list-style: none; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0;">
                    <li>✓ React/Next.js Architecture</li>
                    <li>✓ Database Design & API Dev</li>
                    <li>✓ User Authentication & Roles</li>
